(541, 'FAIZ SIDDIQUI', 'faiz@orchidtobacco.com', '+971554530226', 'TAB EXPO', 'GENEVA', NULL, '45SQM', '3', 'dubai', 'Dear Stand Contractor,\r\n\r\nWe will be participating in the TAB EXPO 2025, which will be held on May 8-9 in Geneva, Switzerland. \r\n\r\nOur Stand No is E15\r\n\r\nI have attached two design options for our stand, and we are aiming for a very basic yet functional layout.\r\n\r\nOption 1:\r\n\r\nLayout Overview:\r\n\r\nOverall Dimensions: 9m (Width) x 5m (Depth)\r\nPartition Wall:\r\n\r\nHeight: 1.5m\r\nLength: 3m (horizontal) + 2m (vertical) for separation\r\nTV mounted on partition wall\r\nRaised Flooring\r\nReception Areas:\r\n\r\nTwo reception counters placed at opposite corners of the front side\r\nCompact counters designed for visitor welcoming\r\nSeating Arrangements:\r\n\r\nTable & Chair Seating (4-person sets): Two seating areas on each side for discussions and meetings\r\nCompact Sofa Seating (4-person sets): Two lounge-style seating areas for informal conversations\r\nPartition Wall with TV:\r\n\r\n3m horizontal section and 2m vertical section with a mounted TV for presentations or promotional videos\r\nBranding & Graphics:\r\n\r\nLarge logo and branding displayed on the partition wall\r\nReception desk branding for easy identification\r\nLighting:\r\n\r\nExtra spotlights focused on the TV area and reception desks\r\nAmbient lighting for seating areas\r\nMaterial & Color Scheme:\r\n\r\nWhite walls with red LED stripes\r\nModern, sleek furniture with a professional finish\r\nA stylish contrast of light and dark elements\r\nOption 2\r\n\r\nThis 2D stand design features a 9m x 5m rectangular layout optimized for seating and engagement. The space includes four sofa seating areas, each accommodating four people, arranged symmetrically for comfort and accessibility.\r\n\r\nA solid wall is positioned at the back, likely for branding, presentations, or display purposes. The front section incorporates strategic lighting placements to enhance visib