(590, 'Chi Nguyen', 'chi.nguyen@alteams.com', '+358408723782', 'Euroguss 2026', 'Nuremberg', NULL, '42 m2', '1', 'Finland', 'Hello,\r\n\r\nMy name is Chi Nguyen, and I am the Marketing Manager at Alteams – an aluminium casting company based in Finland. We are currently looking for a booth design and construction partner for our upcoming participation in EUROGUSS 2026 in Nuremberg.\r\nOur booth will be 42 m² (7 x 6 meters) with two open sides. Using the organizer\'s configurator, I’ve been able to create a rough visual of the kind of look we’re aiming for. \r\nCould you please share your  pricing details, and any standard packages you offer for a booth of this size? We are particularly interested in a modern, professional design that reflects our brand and technical expertise.\r\nLooking forward to your reply.', '2025-06-18 12:50:10', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '217.152.185.129'),
(591, 'Anna Meldgaard Hansen', 'anna.hansen@3shape.com', '+4522974394', 'EUHA 2025', 'Nuremberg', NULL, '3x8', '5', 'Denmark', 'Hello,\r\n3Shape Audio is exhibiting at EUHA 2025, which takes place from October 22–24 in NCC-Ost, Messe Center in Nuremberg.\r\n\r\nI am reaching out to you as I am currently gathering quotes for the construction of our exhibition stand. Would you be interested in making us an offer? \r\n\r\nOur stand dimensions are 3 meters x 8 meters, a corner booth opening to the left side.\r\n\r\nPlease find attached our brand guidelines, technical regulations, and a stand construction briefing outlining the specifications, functional requirements, the hall plan, and the layout we are imagining for our stand.\r\n\r\nWhat we are looking for:\r\n\r\n•	A detailed quote with clearly specified prices for all construction and design elements\r\n•	Expert input on construction and design options that best support our desired functionality, aesthetics, and brand identity\r\n•	Close collaboration and ongoing guidance throughout the project to ensure alignment with our vision and practical needs\r\n•	Regular status meetings to review progress, address questions, and adjust plans as needed\r\n•	Budget awareness: While we have high ambitions for the stand, we are working within a limited budget (< EUR 15.000). Your input on cost-saving opportunities that don’t compromise quality, or impact will be greatly appreciated\r\n\r\nWe are looking to move forward swiftly and would be grateful to receive your proposal - including initial ideas and a quote as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nLet me know if you have any questions or if you need anything else from me.\r\n\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\nBest regards,\r\nAnna Meldgaard Hansen\r\nGrowth Marketing Manager\r\n3Shape Audio', '2025-06-20 06:29:17', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '195.49.232.27'),
