(594, 'Eugenie Ellor', 'eellor@outsourcedevents.com', '+44 (0)123 456 7890', 'Verint - Beyond Boundaries', 'Barcelona', NULL, '5m x 5m', '4', 'United Kingdom', 'I\'m reaching out to enquire whether you would be able to assist with a booth build for our client, Verint, at the Museu Maritm de Barcelona in the Sala Gran space from 13th to 15th October. \r\n\r\nWe would appreciate it if you could provide a quote based on the following requirements:\r\n\r\no	Stand space – 5m x 5m stand \r\no	3 open sides stand space \r\no	Printing and building the stand \r\no	2 x demo pods with large monitors with stools \r\no	1 blue or white 2-seater settee and 2 chairs \r\no	1 small table with 4 chairs. \r\no	Hire of 2 monitors \r\no	Lightboxes and lighting for the stand\r\no	Ensure there is enough space for the demos \r\n\r\nSet up will be on Monday 13th and derig will be on evening of 15th. \r\n\r\nI have attached some examples of the booths Verint had had in the past, so that you can see the type of graphics they go for. \r\n\r\nI have also attached the floorplan to show where the booth is going to be placed. \r\n\r\nLet me know if this is something you can help with.', '2025-06-24 09:09:29', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '212.161.80.58'),
(595, 'Joseph Gurnett', 'joe.gurnett@europebbletec.com', '960429071', 'Salon Sett', 'Montpellier', NULL, '30', '', 'Portugal', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI hope this message finds you well.\r\n\r\nWe are currently exploring options for our exhibition setup and wanted to ask if your company offers a service that includes the installation of an exhibition stand, with the possibility of storing the set and reusing it for future events.\r\n\r\nWe exhibit every year at Salon Sett in Montpellier, with this year’s edition taking place from November 4–6, 2025. We are looking for a long-term solution where the stand can be kept in storage between events and reinstalled annually.\r\n\r\nCould you please let us know if this is something you offer, and if so, provide more details on how the process works, including costs, storage terms, and lead times?\r\n\r\nLooking forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nJoseph\r\n\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\n\r\nBonjour,\r\nJ’espère que vous allez bien.\r\n\r\nNous sommes actuellement à la recherche de solutions pour notre stand d’exposition et souhaitons savoir si votre entreprise propose un service d’installation de stand, avec la possibilité de stocker le matériel et de le réutiliser lors de nos participations futures.\r\n\r\nNous exposons chaque année au Salon Sett à Montpellier, dont la prochaine édition aura lieu du 4 au 6 novembre 2025. Nous cherchons une solution à long terme permettant de conserver le stand en stockage entre les éditions et de le réinstaller chaque année.\r\n\r\nPourriez-vous nous indiquer si ce service fait partie de votre offre, et le cas échéant, nous fournir plus d’informations sur les modalités, les coûts, les conditions de stockage et les délais à prévoir ?\r\n\r\nDans l’attente de votre retour.\r\n\r\nBien cordialement,\r\nJoseph', '2025-06-25 15:10:34', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '94.202.240.149'),
