(602, 'Ana Martinez', 'ana@terranostra.com', '(650) 681-8985', 'Biofach 2026', 'nuremberg', NULL, '25 m2', '1', 'USA', 'Here’s a quick overview of the specs we have in mind:\r\nBooth type: Corner booth\r\nSize: 25 m²\r\nMaterials preferred:\r\n - LED lighting\r\n - Printed vinyl for branding\r\n - Wood or aluminum structure\r\n - White acrylic for niches\r\n (Open to more cost-effective alternatives)\r\nProduct display:\r\n - ~24 items\r\n - Displayed in plates or jars\r\n - Each approx. 12 cm high\r\n - All inside niches\r\nMeeting space:\r\n - 3 areas with tables and chairs (or maybe a sofa setup)\r\nLet me know if you\'re available for a call next  week on Tuesday or Wednesday morning (CET) — we’re flexible, so feel free to suggest another time if needed.\r\nAlso, I\'m attaching a photo of our space, a video, and a photo of a booth we like — to give you a better idea of the direction we\'re thinking.', '2025-07-03 17:28:16', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '38.77.71.10'),
