(611, 'Ahmed Hisham', 'ahmed@fractal.ae', '+97152 868 2160', 'WTM London', 'London', NULL, '120sqm', '1', 'UAE', 'Stand Specs:\r\n\r\n- Dimensions: 15m L x 8m W, rectangular, open on three sides with one 15-meter side closed.\r\n- Flooring: PVC floor, 10cm raised as per design, with an LED strip around the entire floor (as per design).\r\n- Reception Area: Lockable reception desk, plants, 3D backlit logo, and two black high stools (as per design).\r\n- Seating Areas: Three to four seating areas, each with a table and four chairs of the same color and shape (as per design).\r\n\r\nBar Area:\r\n\r\n- Lockable bar counter with six bar chairs (as per design).\r\n- Back bar wall with three LED-lit shelves (as per design).\r\n- Lockable storage area below the back wall (as per design).\r\n\r\nStores:\r\n\r\n- Two main stores with doors:\r\n* Right Store: Fully functional sink, dishwasher, and storage cabinets (as per design). Please note that all functional water pumps, drainage, and water tanks will be provided by us and are not to be included in your cost.\r\n* Left Store: Wooden shelves with multiple layers (as per design).\r\n\r\nCeiling:\r\n\r\n- Approximate dimensions: 13m x 5m.\r\n- Two 3D backlit logos.\r\n- Fabric material with LED lighting.\r\n- Six layers for a rounded wooden frame with fabric and lighting.\r\n- Fabric color degree: v303.\r\n- Alternative: Please provide a separate price quotation if the entire ceiling were made of wooden material instead of fabric.\r\n\r\nLounge Area (Left Side):\r\n\r\n- Decoration as per design, including sofa, theme, table, lights, and overall theme.\r\n\r\nCorners:\r\n\r\n- Stand left and right corners to include stones, greenery, trees, and 3D backlit logos (as per design).\r\n- All plants and greenery will be used as per design.\r\n\r\nAV System (Average Price per sqm):\r\n\r\n- Wall LED Screen (resolution P2.5mm & P1.9mm).\r\n- Floor LED Screen (resolution P3.9mm).', '2025-07-10 14:30:48', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quot