(615, 'Arif Yasa', 'arif@carisatravel.com', '+358400470772', 'EAIE 2025', 'Gothenburg', NULL, '24 m x 9 m : 216 m²', '1', 'Finland', 'Below is a detailed description of the work. Please email me your offer or any question you may have.\r\nTYPE OF SERVICE – DESCRIPTION\r\nExhibition Stand Construction and Dismantling:\r\nA 216 m² area will be used to construct an exhibition stand based on the specifications below and the design provided in Annex I. The stand will be assembled in the exhibition area and dismantled after the fair. (All work will be done on a rental basis.)\r\n \r\nA) CONSTRUCTION WORKS\r\n1.	Flooring:\r\no	Carpet installation for 216 m² (2325.01 sq ft) area using RIP carpet.\r\n2.	Walls:\r\no	The exhibition stand will be built according to the approved design by the central authority. It will be constructed from scratch on a rented bare space, including full assembly and dismantling.\r\no	A storage area (450x200x250 cm) will be created with a 1300 cm long and 250 cm high wall.\r\n3.	Hanging Signboard:\r\no	An illuminated hanging signboard sized 1600x400x80(h) cm will be installed in the stand area according to the fair center’s approval. These are approximate dimensions based on the design in Annex I and may vary by ±1 meter based on EAIE’s instructions or requirements.\r\nB) ELECTRICAL WORKS\r\n1.	Infrastructure Setup:\r\no	Complete electrical infrastructure for the stand.\r\n2.	Electrical Panel (Including Fuses):\r\no	A centralized electrical panel for all circuits in the stand.\r\n3.	Switches and Sockets:\r\no	First-class grounded sockets, light switches, and data sockets installed where needed.\r\no	Electrical connections and sockets at all university desks.\r\no	10 extension cords (3 meters, 4 outlets), and 1 extension cord (10 meters, 4 outlets).\r\n4.	General Lighting – Spotlights:\r\no	Wiring and installation of spotlights as per the project plan.\r\n5.	Track Lighting – Spotlights:\r\no	Wiring and installation of track spotlights as per the project plan.\r\nC) GRAPHIC AND VISUAL WORKS\r\n1.	Colored Vinyl and Digital Printing:\r\no	Digital printing on designated wall surfaces, counters, table fronts/backs, under-table fronts, outer walls of storage, and existing columns up to 250 cm height.\r\no	First-class printing materials will be used and approved by the administration in advance.\r\n2.	Front Counter Prints:\r\no	Digital prints to cover entire counter fronts, using first-class materials and pre-approved designs.\r\nFURNITURE AND ELECTRONIC EQUIPMENT\r\n1.	Furniture for Open Stand Area:\r\no	8 bar stools (adjustable, wheeled, soft black ergonomic fabric)\r\no	4 counters (1.4m x 0.5m, with internal shelves and hidden power sockets)\r\no	43 meeting tables for universities, with 4 chairs per table\r\n(tables will be used interchangeably and designs can be updated as needed)\r\n	Posters provided by universities will be displayed: 50x50 cm (front), 50x120 cm (back), 50x70 cm (bottom front).\r\n	86 universities will rotate usage of the tables.\r\no	4 triple brochure stands\r\no	4 round tables (first-class wood, 120 cm width, 75 cm height)\r\n	Each with hidden power sockets and triple outlets\r\no	16 desk chairs (wheeled, adjustable height, soft black texture)\r\no	2 freestanding university layout signs (80x200 cm)\r\no	Sample counter, round table with chairs, university table and chairs, bar stool', '2025-07-24 07:57:42', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '93.106.11.220'),
