(620, 'Prince Rasheed Kareem', 'admin@globalmirrortnt.com', '3602077803', 'CMT-The Holiday Exhibition 2026', 'Stuttgart', NULL, '10 by 10', '', 'USA', 'Subject: Request for Exhibition Price List and Invitation Letter for Upcoming Travel & Tourism Exhibition in Germany\r\nDear Organizer,\r\nI am the proprietor of Global Mirror Travel and Tour, registered as a DBA in the State of Texas, USA, and also operate under Global Mirror Travel and Tours Ltd in Nigeria.\r\nWe are interested in participating in your upcoming travel and tourism exhibition in Germany to showcase our specialty tour packages across East, West, North, and South Africa, as well as destinations in the USA (including Alaska, Hawaii, and Florida), and the Caribbean.\r\nAdditionally, we intend to exhibit our innovative GlidSit Smart Bag, a newly invented travel accessory designed for traveler comfort, developed under a conditional patent/trademark. This exhibition will provide an excellent platform for both promotion and sales of this new product.\r\nKindly provide us with:\r\nA detailed price list for exhibition booths or participation packages.\r\nA letter of invitation for our Nigeria-based delegates/staff applying for a German\r\nvisa at the German Consulate in Lagos.\r\nA letter of invitation for myself (a U.S. permanent resident) to facilitate a Schengen visa application from the USA.\r\nThank you for your consideration. We look forward to your positive response.\r\nWarm regards,\r\nCEO: Prince Rasheed Kareem\r\nProprietor, Global Mirror Travel and Tour\r\nEmail: admin@globalmirrortnt.com\r\nPhone: 360-207-7803', '2025-08-14 02:11:32', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '172.56.109.82');
