(625, 'Aaron Levitanus', 'aaron@genorayeurope.com', '17615169989', 'Fachdental Stuttgart', 'Stuttgart, Germany', NULL, '21 m²', '1', 'Germany', 'Dear Radon Team,\r\nMy name is Aaron Levitanus, and I am writing to you on behalf of Genoray EU GmbH. \r\nI would like to request a quote for a reusable exhibition booth. We have an existing design that can be used as a reference; we are looking for a similar concept.\r\n\r\nWe will be exhibiting at the following two events this year:\r\n\r\nFachdental Stuttgart: October 10-11, 2025  \r\nBooth number 8B39\r\nhttps://fileshare.lms-cloud.de/index.php/s/FLnALgTPSAz4q5z?dir=/&editing=false&openfile=true\r\n\r\nFachdental Frankfurt: November 7-8, 2025  \r\nBooth number 5.0C57\r\nhttps://fileshare.lms-cloud.de/index.php/s/nMHsHyeYRyfcY6P?dir=/&editing=false&openfile=true\r\nFor both events, the booth size is 3x7 meters and it is a corner stand.\r\nA key requirement is that the booth be reusable. We plan to use it for these two shows and for several other German exhibitions next year. Therefore, could you please confirm if your services include storing the booth between events and managing its transportation to each venue?\r\n\r\nTo help guide your proposal, our budget for the initial production and first-time setup of the booth is in the range of €10,000 to €15,000. For subsequent exhibitions, we anticipate the cost for re-installation (including transport and setup) to be significantly lower. We would appreciate it if your quote could provide a clear breakdown of these separate costs.  \r\nPlease find our existing booth design attached for your reference.\r\nThank you for your assistance. We look forward to receiving your proposal.\r\nBest regards,\r\nAaron Levitanus | Sales Coordinator\r\nGenoray EU GmbH\r\naaron@genorayeurope.com\r\nMob: +49 176 15169989\r\nDorotheenstr. 54 | 10117 Berlin | Germany\r\nwww.genoray.com | +49 30 50969498', '2025-08-21 12:44:19', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '84.172.92.144'),
