(690, 'Lisa Martin', 'lisa@sublimedata.us', '2019990127', 'NA', 'Des Moines', NULL, '0', '', 'United States', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nHope you’re doing well.\r\n\r\nWe support exhibition stand design and construction companies by providing accurate B2B contact data of exhibitors participating in exhibitions and trade shows worldwide. This helps you connect directly with companies that actively plan and invest in exhibition booths.\r\n\r\nOur database covers exhibitors from major and regional trade shows across the globe, segmented by industry, country, show name, and participation history. This allows you to approach the right brands before upcoming events and for future exhibitions.\r\n\r\nYou can reach teams such as: Marketing Managers • Event & Exhibition Managers • Brand Heads • Trade Marketing Leads • Procurement Teams • Business Development Directors & other decision makers.\r\n\r\nClients use this data to plan pre-show outreach, post-show follow-ups, and long-term exhibitor engagement, while maintaining a clean, CRM-ready contact list across multiple regions.\r\n\r\nIf you’d like, share the shows, regions, or industries you’re focusing on, and I’ll be happy to send a few sample contacts so you can review the format and quality.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nLisa Martin\r\n\r\nP.S. To unsubscribe, please reply with \"Unsubscribe', '2025-12-22 15:36:39', NULL, 'Quotation Form', '/quotation-form/', '223.178.208.160'),
